title: Packers Punished by NFL, Ravens QB Lamar Jackson in MVP Race, #FreeOdell?, Which contender will lose in NFL Week 10?
itunes:title: Packers Punished by NFL, Ravens QB Lamar Jackson in MVP Race, #FreeOdell?, Which contender will lose in NFL Week 10?
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager and LeSean McCoy discuss the NFL issuing fines to the Packers and QB Aaron Rodgers. Ravens QB Lamar Jackson is solidly in the middle of the MVP race alongside Tom Brady and Kyler Murray. LeSean McCoy explains what the #FreeOdell movement is all about. Kay makes some Fantasy Football choices on 'Which Guy Wednesday' and what will be the most remarkable story to come out of NFL Week 10?

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
